To install this package, you need:

  * Ruby
  * Ruby-GNOME2
  * SQLLite3-Ruby

The installation is simple. As root, run:

  # ruby install.rb

To install in a custom directory, run:

  # ruby install.rb --share-dir /usr/share/gladius --bin-dir /usr/bin

To uninstall, run:

  # ruby install.rb --uninstall
